{"tid":1187194,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[iOS 13]  窮撚福音","createTime":"2019-06-05T13:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:28:49.000Z","uid":109383,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"834634f05eaf79425845b30ef0deceff66bd8044","tid":1187194,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"iOS 13 有不少新功能是在 Apple 發佈會沒有提到。當中一項名為 Smart Battery Charging 功能相同值得留意。iOS 13 用戶，現在到「電池健康度」除了可看到你的電池健康值，也可看到一項名為「最佳化電池充電」的選項，啟動後能有助減慢電池老化速度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 會學習你的每日充電模式，充電到 80% 時會等待充電完成，直到你需要使用 iPhone 為止。<br />\n<br />\n舉例說，當 iPhone 知道你每天 6 時起床，那麼晚上充電到 80% 時便會暫停，等待你起床前 2 小時（4：００時）才開始 80% 至 100% 的一段充電，令你不會太早充到 100%，而降回電量又重新再充電，減少有限的充電次數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_1118.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FIMG_1118.jpeg&h=ae9c3378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_1119.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FIMG_1119.jpeg&h=b9e7273b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"270b88ee109df7fd591962228bea031f1298207a","tid":1187194,"uid":109383,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"iPhone 6S 又可以再戰3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e19d6fde975a918074da1e4eee7bd6d110da18","tid":1187194,"uid":20890,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"咁我就可以放心差爆電訓覺"},{"pid":"2f37412053cd901b735b5bdbedbec36805f1894f","tid":1187194,"uid":238660,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"270b88ee109df7fd591962228bea031f1298207a","tid":1187194,"uid":109383,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"iPhone 6S 又可以再戰3年<img s